=> command line argumment parsing:
	-> -h --help			(print help)
	-> -G --GUI				(use GUI window, default)
	-> -C --CLI				(display in the terminal)
	-> -D --DEBUG 			(show debug information)
	-> -s --scale [amount]	(set window scale, GUI only)
	-> -g --grid 			(show pixel gird, GUI only)

